<h1 class='pageTitle'>{{title}}</h1>

<div id='mainContentDiv'>
    <!--<div id='mainContentOverlay'>-->
        <h2 id='mainContentOverlay'>Who am I? Click through the dates to find out.</h2> 
    <!--</div>-->
    <div id='imageContainer'>
        <img id='mainContentImage' class='mainImage' src='/images/jamie_square.png' alt='mainImage'>
    </div>
    <div id='textContainer'>
        <h2 id='mainContentHeader' class='mainContentText'></h2>
        <p id='mainContentP' class='mainContentText'></p>
    </div>
</div>

<div id='timeline'>
    {{#each timeline}}
        <div class='timelineItem'>
            <h2 class='timelineItemHeader timelineItemHidden'>{{title}}</h2>
            <p class='timelineItemImgSrc timelineItemHidden'>{{imgsrc}}</p>
            <p class='timelineItemDesc timelineItemHidden'>{{desc}}</p>
            <p class='timelineItemYear'>{{year}}</p>
        </div>
    {{/each}}
</div> 
<div id='arrowContainer'>
    <img id='scrollArrow' src='/images/arrow.png' alt='scroll arrow'>
</div>
<div class='sectionTwo'>
    <h2 class='sectionTitle'>What gets me out of bed?</h2>
    <p class='sectionTwoP'>I love science in all it's forms.  The way of thinking it provides, the way it seeks elegance, rather than complexity, and the appreciation it grants for the natural world. Because of this vast appreciation for what this kind of knowledge can provide, I want to spread that to the broadest audience possible with that hopes that it will help us solve some of the worlds greatest problems.  In particular, I'm passionate about Climate Change and trying to understand how I can leverage the web and mobile platforms to educate and disseminate accurate information in an engaging way. </p>
    <h2 class='sectionTitle'>Skills</h2>
    <div id='skillsDiv'>
        <div class='skill'>
            <h3 class='skillHeader'>Full Stack Web</h3>
            <div class='skillList'>
                <ul>
                    <li>HTML, CSS/Sass, Javascript</li>
                    <li>Node.js with Express framework</li>
                    <li>Templating with Handlebars and Jade</li>
                    <li>MongoDB</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class='skill'>
            <h3 class='skillHeader'>Mobile</h3>
            <div class='skillList'>
                <ul>
                    <li>Swift</li>
                    <li>Working knowledge of Obj-c</li>
                    <li>Cordova</li>
                    <li>Parse</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class='skill'>
            <h3 class='skillHeader'>Prototyping &amp; Design</h3>
            <div class='skillList'>
                <ul>
                    <li>Arduino &amp; Basic Electronics</li>
                    <li>3D Modeling &amp; Printing</li>
                    <li>Illustrator, Premiere, After Effects</li>
                    <li>Fabrication</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

